{"tid":2320952,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港電台：賽諾菲疫苗測試結果對年長人士產生的免疫能力較低","createTime":"2020-12-11T07:45:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T08:00:38.000Z","uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"72285c1640ca2a5a2e3606206dcee6e30bd1f285","tid":2320952,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T07:45:20.000Z","msg":"法國藥廠賽諾菲和英國葛蘭素史克表示，<strong>中期結果顯示，他們共同研發的新型冠狀病毒疫苗，對年長人士產生的免疫能力較低</strong>，需要推遲疫苗推出時間，他們計劃在明年展開另一項研究，並期望明年年底前推出更有效的疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n賽諾菲副行政總裁說，對推遲生產疫苗感到失望，但所有決定都是始於科學和數據，強調非常關注公共衛生，有信心能夠生產有效的疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564795-20201211.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564795-20201211.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqUkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=2e08f2ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564795-20201211.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=61831688\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564795-20201211.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"79fe10cab72876a28ea91ffc7169cd510216c969","tid":2320952,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T07:46:19.000Z","msg":"比小朋友打好過啦<br />\n天滅廢老仲想逆天而行"},{"pid":"a090d6266ddc6cc146c12686a3e90f490fe5b4f1","tid":2320952,"uid":170160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79fe10cab72876a28ea91ffc7169cd510216c969","tid":2320952,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T07:46:19.000Z","msg":"比小朋友打好過啦<br />\n天滅廢老仲想逆天而行"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T07:49:46.000Z","msg":"反正好多廢老都唔中意戴口罩，咪由得佢地升天囉 !"},{"pid":"a9da7a754585a5820cead66dbad2a08b6226bbb3","tid":2320952,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T07:56:05.000Z","msg":"疫苗半年就出到<br />\n睇見都驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj